title: Air Force accepting nominations for 2016 O'Malley Award (USAF - United States Air Force)
text: ( Source : USAF - United States Air Force ) JOINT BASE SAN ANTONIO-RANDOLPH, Texas ( AFNS ) -- Air Force Personnel Center officials will accept nominations for the 2016 General and Mrs. Jerome F. O'Malley Award through Jan. 28. The award
